    "![](images/clipboard-14447961.png){fig-align=\"center\"}\n",
    "\n",
    "## Varianza y desviaciÃ³n estÃ¡ndar\n",
    "\n",
    "</br></br>\n",
    "\n",
    "La [**varianza teÃ³rica**]{style=\"color: #5E7D6A\"} de una variable aleatoria continua $X$ es\n",
    "\n",
    "$$V(X) = E\\left[ (X - \\mu)^2 \\right] = \\int_{-\\infty}^\\infty (x-\\mu)^2f(x)dx,$$\n",
    "\n",
